ikh hob dem HONOR OF makhn haynt a intervyu in der nomen fun THE FOUNDATION VISUAL HISTORY FOR SURVIVORS.

15
00:01:36,216 --> 00:01:43,213
haynt, merts dem tsentn, nayntsn hundert nayn zeks un nayntsik do in BNEY-BARAK,

16
00:01:43,438 --> 00:01:47,949
un mit ayer erloybenish veln mir onfangen dem intervyu.

17
00:01:47,949 --> 00:01:52,478
bite, dertseylt mir vos ir gedenkt fun der heym,

18
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:56,696
fun der familye, vi s'hot zikh gelebt far der milkhome. bite.

19
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,417
nokh fun undzer shtetl?

20
00:01:57,994 --> 00:01:59,143
yo, bite.

21
00:02:00,094 --> 00:02:02,535
s'iz gevezn a kleyn shtetl,

22
00:02:03,030 --> 00:02:05,589
nisht keyn sakh FAMILIES,

23
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:10,376
ober s'iz gevezn a shtetl mit a rov, mit a shames, mit a

24
00:02:10,376 --> 00:02:16,338
shoykhet, mit a khazn un dos alts iz gevorn oysgehaltn fun dem shtetl.

25
00:02:17,087 --> 00:02:23,409
natirlekh, s'iz nisht geven keyn zeyer raykh ober s'iz ge-, me hot es oysgehaltn, di kehile hot dos alts oysgehaltn.

26
00:02:24,728 --> 00:02:27,155
s'iz geven a balbatish lebn,

27
00:02:27,330 --> 00:02:30,193
a fayn lebn, nisht geven keyn groyse

28
00:02:30,570 --> 00:02:34,006
tsu fil negidim, s'iz nisht geven keyn sakh oreme-layt,

29
00:02:34,047 --> 00:02:39,221
azoy. iber hoypt, der, di yidish, yidn zenen gevezn sokhrim.

30
00:02:39,312 --> 00:02:43,929
yeder hot gehat a, a kleyt, zay- zayn gesheft,

31
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:48,013
a gevelb, in mitn mark zenen geven di yidishe gesheftn

32
00:02:48,070 --> 00:02:51,180
un dos iz geven di parnose.

33
00:02:51,180 --> 00:02:55,069
yeder hot gehat, eyner ⟨aza⟩ kleyt, eyner aza s- UNK,

34
00:02:55,069 --> 00:02:57,277
dos iz geven di yidishe parnose.

35
00:02:57,351 --> 00:03:00,990
un got a dank, s'iz geven biz der milkhome iz gevezn

36
00:03:01,182 --> 00:03:05,864
zeyer gut, di ga-, di ale yidn hobn gelebt azoy vi eyn mishpokhe.

37
00:03:05,864 --> 00:03:11,884
s'iz geven a simkhe, zenen ale zikh tsuzamengekumen: der rov, un der khazn, un der shoykhet

38
00:03:11,886 --> 00:03:14,366
un a- un di yidn, di kehile.

39
00:03:14,366 --> 00:03:21,378
un s'iz geven di zelbe zakh, a simkhe, a bris, ober alts, un kholile-vekholile es zol nisht geshen az s'iz geven

40
00:03:21,378 --> 00:03:23,757
a tsore hobn ale mitgeveynt.

41
00:03:23,757 --> 00:03:28,024
dos iz geven dos yidishe lebn, dos shtile lebn.

42
00:03:28,148 --> 00:03:34,388
un ⟨es zol geyn⟩ mit di kristn hobn mir oykh nisht shlekht gelebt. mir z- hobn gut gelebt mit zey, zenen gevezn

43
00:03:34,388 --> 00:03:37,304
shkheynim. me ken nisht zogn.

44
00:03:37,834 --> 00:03:40,410
biz di milkhome. me hot zey nisht gehetst.

45
00:03:40,602 --> 00:03:45,593
s'iz geven, dos iz geven di tsore, az me hot zey nisht gehetst, zenen nisht geven k'aza min

46
00:03:45,593 --> 00:03:48,341
inteligent folk vos zey hobn,

47
00:03:48,567 --> 00:03:51,871
zey hobn aleynt farshtanen. az me hot zey,

48
00:03:51,871 --> 00:03:54,756
geganen mit zey in gutn iz undz oykh geven gut.

49
00:03:54,756 --> 00:03:57,161
az me hot zey gehetst zenen zey geven nisht gut.

50
00:03:57,161 --> 00:03:59,017
letstns ven s'iz geven shoyn

51
00:03:59,017 --> 00:04:04,983
far der milkhome az me hot shoyn geredt azoy vegn der milkhome hobn zey shoyn gehat mer khutspe.

52
00:04:04,983 --> 00:04:10,965
hobn zey shoyn mer ongehoybn tsu boykotirn, nisht tsu kumen in di yidishe gesheftn,

53
00:04:10,965 --> 00:04:13,023
un s'iz shoyn geven nisht azoy gut.

54
00:04:13,023 --> 00:04:19,031
vayl der Hitler, me hot zey gehetst, az Hiter vet kumen vet er, vet er makhn a khurbn.

55
00:04:19,031 --> 00:04:22,361
leyder, leyder hot zikh es farvirklekht.

56
00:04:22,418 --> 00:04:28,750
yetst hob ikh aykh gevolt fray- fregn a kurtse frage, lebn d- vi hot geheysn ayer shtetl?

57
00:04:28,620 --> 00:04:29,584
SKĘPE.

58
00:04:29,587 --> 00:04:31,190
vu iz dos geven, vayt fun Var-...

59
00:04:31,092 --> 00:04:33,096
lebn LIPNO, lebn SIERPC

60
00:04:33,096 --> 00:04:36,249
in di di WOJEWÓDZTWO WARSZAWSKIE.

61
00:04:36,762 --> 00:04:41,211
yetst, ir aleyn hot ir zikh gelernt in epes a shkole far der milkhome?

62
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,189
in a POWSZECHNY shul,

63
00:04:42,499 --> 00:04:44,520
nor in a POWSZECHNY shul.

64
00:04:45,553 --> 00:04:48,382
dermanendik ayer kleyn shtetl, SKĘPE,

65
00:04:47,715 --> 00:04:47,990
ye.

66
00:04:48,777 --> 00:04:55,570
dort iz geven oykh tsienistishe tetikeyt? ir hot geven epes farbundn mit di tsienistishe bavegung? kent ir a bisl dertseyln vegn dem?

67
00:04:52,922 --> 00:04:53,368
ya.

68
00:04:55,130 --> 00:05:00,906
ya, spetsyel, keyn organizatsye, s'iz nisht geven ⟨vayl⟩ s'iz nisht geven a groyser yugnt,

69
00:05:00,906 --> 00:05:04,020
nor der yugnt iz geven tsienistish.

70
00:05:04,020 --> 00:05:09,859
mir hobn geshtrebt ale ⟨nokh⟩ demolt Palestine, demolt iz dokh nokh nisht geven Yisroel.

71
00:05:09,330 --> 00:05:09,982
rikhtik.

72
00:05:09,957 --> 00:05:12,688
hobn ale ge- gesh- ge-

73
00:05:12,574 --> 00:05:13,229
geshtrebt.

74
00:05:13,030 --> 00:05:14,867
geshtrebt nokh dem, yo.

75
00:05:15,169 --> 00:05:20,245
iz ikh gedenk, zenen gekumen referentn, flegn kumen un haltn referatn.

76
00:05:20,245 --> 00:05:23,313
fun Yisroel, zey hobn tsuzamengenumen zakhn

77
00:05:23,438 --> 00:05:26,823
un gelt, zilber, gold, gelt

78
00:05:26,847 --> 00:05:29,288
oyf far Kern-Kayemes.

79
00:05:29,900 --> 00:05:33,439
tsu koyfn do in land bodn.

80
00:05:33,597 --> 00:05:38,924
iz yeder eyner iz geven azoy ibergenumen az MAMASH kinder

81
00:05:38,924 --> 00:05:43,724
vos zenen geven, bay undz iz alts forgekumen az s'iz geven a referat iz geven in di shul,

82
00:05:43,772 --> 00:05:46,348
zenen zikh ale tsuzamengekumen in di shul.

83
00:05:46,371 --> 00:05:48,713
⟨zey hobn⟩ zikh tsuzamengekumen

84
00:05:48,713 --> 00:05:54,476
un yeder eyner az ver hot geredt dervegn iz azoy ibergenumen geven dermit,

85
00:05:54,476 --> 00:05:56,383
az me hot, vos me hot gehat

86
00:05:56,383 --> 00:05:58,644
a fingerl, a por oyringlekh,

87
00:05:58,644 --> 00:06:01,268
hot yeder, di di kinder, di meydelekh

88
00:06:01,268 --> 00:06:06,843
fun di tsveyte zayt vos bay undz iz geven a a froyen-shul far ⟨-zunder⟩ un a mener-shul

89
00:06:06,843 --> 00:06:10,580
un durkhn fentster hot men gevorfn dos vos me hot gehat.

90
00:06:10,620 --> 00:06:15,857
az me, yo, tsienistish, me hot ge-, ale tsienistish. s'iz nisht geven keyn andere parteyen.

91
00:06:15,857 --> 00:06:18,630
in di gresere shtet iz yo, s'iz geven parteyen.

92
00:06:18,630 --> 00:06:21,730
s'iz geven bundistn, s'iz geven pale-tsienistn,

93
00:06:21,730 --> 00:06:24,604
bay undz zenen ale mir gevezn tsienistn.

94
00:06:23,952 --> 00:06:25,329
klal-tsienistn.

95
00:06:24,829 --> 00:06:29,581
ale, zey hobn ge- geshtrebt nokh Yisroel. me hot nisht gevust epes andersh.

96
00:06:30,651 --> 00:06:32,467
yetst

97
00:06:33,823 --> 00:06:37,975
tsu aykh iz ongekumen in shtot arayn ayer shvester fun ergets vu?

98
00:06:37,975 --> 00:06:41,174
vi, vi dos pasirt? vos kent ir mir dertseyln vegn dem?

99
00:06:39,510 --> 00:06:40,310
yo.

100
00:06:40,612 --> 00:06:45,782
di, mayn shvester, ikh hob ge- di eltste shvester mayne hot gevoynt in Hamburg in Daytshland.

101
00:06:45,872 --> 00:06:50,248
iz azoy vi me hot oysgevizn di yidn fun Daytshland

102
00:06:50,248 --> 00:06:54,776
zenen geven poylishe birger, hot men zey geshikt nokh ZBĄSZYŃ.

103
00:06:55,137 --> 00:06:59,923
un demolt zey, zey zenen nisht geforn nokh ZBĄSZYŃ, zenen zey gekumen tsu undz,

104
00:06:59,929 --> 00:07:01,555
mir d-, nokh SKĘPE.

105
00:07:01,555 --> 00:07:06,167
un zenen geven mit undz tsuzamen biz me hot undz geyogt aroys fun SKĘPE.

106
00:07:04,857 --> 00:07:08,508
un dos hot ge-, dos hot pasirt in zeks un draysikstn?

107
00:07:07,877 --> 00:07:11,971
zibn un draysikstn, meyn ikh, iz es geven, yo, ikh meyn az yo.

108
00:07:08,508 --> 00:07:10,583
zibn un draysikstn yor.

109
00:07:10,583 --> 00:07:16,241
vos hobn zey, vos flegn zey dertseyln vegn Daytshland? vegn di tsores vos Hitler hot zey ongemakh-?

110
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:17,287
zey hobn nisht fartseylt, zey hobn moyre gehat tsu redn.

111
00:07:17,580 --> 00:07:21,930
zey hobn moyre gehat tsu redn, ober dos vos zey hobn gezogt az s'iz shlekht, s'iz nisht gut,

112
00:07:21,930 --> 00:07:25,210
az me hot zey aroysgeyogt, zey hobn shoyn nisht ⟨gekont, az zey hobn⟩ ales tsugenumen,

113
00:07:25,210 --> 00:07:27,905
m'iz gekumen bay der nakht un m'hot zey aroysgeyogt,

114
00:07:28,695 --> 00:07:29,284
shoyn.

115
00:07:30,051 --> 00:07:35,310
nor dos iz geven a nes bay undz, a nes, s'iz leyder nisht geven shoyn shpeter keyn nes,

116
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:39,379
vos mayn shvester iz grade gevezn oyf a bazukh bay undz,

117
00:07:39,379 --> 00:07:41,219
hot zi gehat dos rekht

118
00:07:41,219 --> 00:07:45,739
tsuriktsuforn un zikh nokh tsu nemen vos zi hot ge- vos zi hot gehat.

119
00:07:45,863 --> 00:07:49,648
az zi iz gekumen shoyn dos tsveyte mol, vos zi hot shoyn gemuzt avek

120
00:07:49,648 --> 00:07:51,864
hot zi mitgebrengt zeyer a sakh

121
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:57,350
zilbervarg, bashtek, mit zeyer a sakh zakhn.

122
00:07:55,718 --> 00:07:56,990
me hot zi nokh demolts,

123
00:07:56,990 --> 00:07:58,716
me hot ir nor demolts aroysgelozt.

124
00:07:57,350 --> 00:08:00,650
yo, zi hot gekont aroy-, yo, zi hot gekont aroysfirn.

125
00:08:00,650 --> 00:08:03,558
meyle, zey hobn shoyn gevust ⟨az s'vet zayn, zey hobn zikh zeyers⟩.

126
00:08:03,784 --> 00:08:06,528
hot zi ge- dos ales gebrengt legal.

127
00:08:06,653 --> 00:08:11,737
nu, ⟨undz ho'mir gemuzt⟩ SOWIESO shpeter avekgegebn tsu kristn, me hot zi shoyn mer nisht opgekrign,

128
00:08:11,737 --> 00:08:13,599
me hot mer nisht opgekrign.

129
00:08:14,128 --> 00:08:17,441
shoyn, UNK iz dos iz shoyn nisht gevezn in di, SOWIESO.

130
00:08:17,441 --> 00:08:20,602
zi hot gebrengt, ober, s'iz shoyn gornisht geven.

131
00:08:19,546 --> 00:08:20,229
yo.

132
00:08:20,980 --> 00:08:23,758
iz zi geblibn lebn mit aykh in dem shtetl.

133
00:08:23,190 --> 00:08:26,223
zi iz geblibn mit undz in shtetl biz me hot undz

134
00:08:26,223 --> 00:08:31,529
in akht un... in nayn un, nayn un draysikstn iz gevezn ven me hot undz geyogt, yo.

135
00:08:29,468 --> 00:08:30,052
yo,

136
00:08:30,852 --> 00:08:35,170
bizn nayn un dray-, biz di milkhome hot zikh ongehoybn iz nokh epes do vos ir gedenkt

137
00:08:35,170 --> 00:08:39,857
tsu dertseyln vegn yid- vegn yidishn lebn dortn, vegn vos s'hot pasirt dortn bay aykh?

138
00:08:37,325 --> 00:08:39,470
s'iz geve- ah

139
00:08:39,470 --> 00:08:43,346
spetsyel keyn, bay undz iz nisht geven spetsyel keyn zakhn.

140
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:46,179
me hot zikh zeyer ongehert shlekhte zakhn,

141
00:08:46,179 --> 00:08:49,880
ober spetsyel bay undz in shtetl hot nisht pasirt.

142
00:08:51,979 --> 00:08:58,840
iz, in... september oysgebrokhn, nayn un draysikstn oysgebrokhn di velt-milkhome

143
00:08:56,890 --> 00:08:57,813
yo, yo,

144
00:08:58,726 --> 00:08:59,283
yo.

145
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:01,244
tsvishn Daytshl- UNK un Poyln koydem-kol.

146
00:09:01,244 --> 00:09:03,080
vos gedenkt ir fun yene tsaytn?

147
00:09:02,433 --> 00:09:06,080
demolt zenen mir aroys fun shtetl, m'iz arayn in a dorf,

148
00:09:06,188 --> 00:09:07,515
tsu kristn.

149
00:09:07,993 --> 00:09:11,142
me hot gezogt az der Hitler vet kumen, vet er bald

150
00:09:11,385 --> 00:09:13,820
ale di di di mener tsunemen.

151
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:15,514
zenen di mener avek

152
00:09:16,127 --> 00:09:20,545
ah stam in a tsveyte shtot, zey hobn nisht gevust tsi s'vet zayn beser, ober m'hot gezogt

153
00:09:20,545 --> 00:09:23,684
vos vet aykh nisht bald zayn mit gants Poyln,

154
00:09:23,684 --> 00:09:28,848
iz bald ⟨ven er vet⟩ kumen, zoln zey nisht zayn, zenen zikh di mener zenen avek in ergets andersh.

155
00:09:28,848 --> 00:09:32,659
un di froyen zenen avek fun shtetl arayn in a dorf,

156
00:09:32,850 --> 00:09:37,133
in derfer, ver es hot gehat bakante kristn, zenen ⟨mir⟩ geganen tsu di kristn.

157
00:09:37,133 --> 00:09:40,170
me hot gezogt, me hot dokh gemeynt az s'vet zayn a milkhome,

158
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:43,846
m'et, tsi m'et shisn, tsi s'vet zayn dos, m'iz aroys.

159
00:09:44,089 --> 00:09:48,320
ober azoy vi zey zenen gekumen arayn s'iz nisht geven gornisht. me hot ⟨zey⟩ nisht geshosn,

160
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:51,306
zenen SOWIESO ongekumen, ⟨zey, un hobn zey⟩ gezogt,

161
00:09:51,306 --> 00:09:55,488
yeder zol zikh, azoy vi zey hobn getrofn, s'iz geven leydik iberal,

162
00:09:55,488 --> 00:09:59,178
yeder zol aheymforn, ver s'iz avekgeforn zol tsurikforn,

163
00:09:59,178 --> 00:10:02,125
m'et zey gornisht tun. zenen mir tsurikgeforn.

164
00:10:02,125 --> 00:10:06,797
azoy vi mir zenen tsurikgekumen, zenen shoyn fun andere shtet vider oykh antlofn,

165
00:10:06,797 --> 00:10:09,567
zenen zey geven bay undz, hobn farnumen undzere

166
00:10:09,567 --> 00:10:11,151
voynungen.

167
00:10:11,207 --> 00:10:14,798
ober gornisht, eyntsikvayz zenen zikh ale tsurikgeforn aheym.

168
00:10:14,798 --> 00:10:18,215
iz shoyn. m'iz vider gezesn, me hot gevart vos vet zayn.

169
00:10:18,215 --> 00:10:20,004
me hot gezen az s'iz shoyn nisht gut.

170
00:10:20,004 --> 00:10:22,417
me hot shoyn nisht getort geyn in di gas arayn,

171
00:10:22,417 --> 00:10:26,784
un me hot shoyn me hot ⟨s'iz bay undz gevezn⟩ in mitn mark iz geven aza

172
00:10:26,784 --> 00:10:28,362
a MATKA BOSKA

173
00:10:28,487 --> 00:10:31,653
aza mi-

174
00:10:31,018 --> 00:10:32,362
ikh veys vos dos iz.

175
00:10:32,031 --> 00:10:36,750
yo, iz geven ah zeyer hoykh oyfgeboyt in mitn mark.

176
00:10:37,262 --> 00:10:39,365
dos hot men bald aropgeshosn.

177
00:10:39,675 --> 00:10:43,314
dos hobn zey bald ⟨azoy ven zey zenen⟩ gekumen, zey hobn dos gegebn a shis deroyf.

178
00:10:43,489 --> 00:10:47,907
der rov iz nisht antlofn, iz geblibn in shtetl, hot men genumen dem rov

179
00:10:47,907 --> 00:10:49,308
un me hot im ge-

180
00:10:49,308 --> 00:10:53,880
mit di ki- tsvey yinglekh hot er gehat, hot men genumen di tsvey yinglekh mitn rov

181
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:56,071
un me hot gegebn zey tsu kern in mark.

182
00:10:56,382 --> 00:10:59,981
dos iz bald geven di ershte por teg vi zey zenen nor ongekumen.

183
00:10:59,981 --> 00:11:04,470
di mener vos zenen nisht geven, zenen zikh eyntsikvayz aheymgekumen

184
00:11:04,470 --> 00:11:06,129
hot men yedern

185
00:11:06,304 --> 00:11:12,575
gegebn zayn arbet un a sakh hot men... s'iz geven a meshugener bay undz hot men im bald avekgeleygt,

186
00:11:13,442 --> 00:11:14,398
a yid.

187
00:11:14,809 --> 00:11:20,197
un shoyn, dos vos s'iz geven biz me hot me hot gevart biz UNK lang ⟨geblibn⟩ dray monatn.

188
00:11:20,197 --> 00:11:23,071
nakher hot men undz ge- genumen nokh Varshe.

189
00:11:23,128 --> 00:11:25,248
me hot undz geyogt nokh Varshe.

190
00:11:25,305 --> 00:11:28,010
ale yidn fu-, ale yidn fun shtetl?

191
00:11:25,693 --> 00:11:29,855
vi me vil, ale, REIN sh-, JUDEN- JUDENREIN.

192
00:11:30,435 --> 00:11:33,179
vos zhe iz, vos zhe hot pasirt mit aykh demoltstn?

193
00:11:32,629 --> 00:11:36,102
demolt zenen mir gev- di mener zenen geganen

194
00:11:36,102 --> 00:11:40,835
mit mit mit... geforn mit furn, demolt iz nokh nisht geven keyn oytos,

195
00:11:40,835 --> 00:11:45,054
zenen zey geforn vayl me hot dokh mitgenumen a bisl vesh, bet-gevant...

196
00:11:45,054 --> 00:11:49,290
un undz froyen hot men ale arayngezetst in a, a vagon

197
00:11:49,290 --> 00:11:52,434
fun a ⟨vintsiker vi⟩ a koleyke, nisht keyn groyse ban

198
00:11:52,660 --> 00:11:56,569
iz ⟨s'iz⟩ geven a vagon, ⟨zenen⟩ mir ale arayn in dem vagon arayn

199
00:11:56,912 --> 00:11:59,752
on, un s'iz nisht geven ⟨keyn⟩ tsu zitsn ⟨tsu⟩ gornisht

200
00:11:59,752 --> 00:12:02,441
un me hot undz bald, ikh mit mayne kinder,

201
00:12:02,582 --> 00:12:06,187
kh'hob gehaltn lebn zikh, nakher ikh hob nokh gehat a shver,

202
00:12:06,312 --> 00:12:08,969
mayn man's a foter, iz er oykh geven,

203
00:12:08,969 --> 00:12:16,582
undz ze'mir ale gezesn. yeder hot zikh gehaltn mit zayn mishpokhe. un azoy zenen mir geforn biz nokh Var- ⟨neyn⟩, nokh nisht nokh Varshe.

204
00:12:16,653 --> 00:12:22,845
far Varshe, vayl di brik, di brik iz geven tsebrokhn, me hot nisht gekont arayngeyn nokh Varshe

205
00:12:22,845 --> 00:12:25,542
mit keyn ferd, mit keyn gornisht.

206
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:29,537
⟨un m'iz⟩ gekumen dort baym NE- NAREW hot es geheysn.

207
00:12:29,537 --> 00:12:38,324
gut, s'iz shoyn geven farfroyrn, a tog befor iz es nokh nisht geven in gantsn farfroyrn, zenen mentshn zenen adurkh, iz zenen dertrunken gevorn.

208
00:12:38,324 --> 00:12:41,906
mir zenen shoyn adurkh iz shoyn geven dos ayz

209
00:12:41,906 --> 00:12:45,399
oyf dem oyf dem NAREW iz shoyn s'iz alts geven gefroyrn.

210
00:12:45,399 --> 00:12:48,240
mir hobn gehat mazl, m'iz adurkh besholem.

211
00:12:48,263 --> 00:12:56,136
ze'mir gekumen, yeder hot gehat emetsn, bakante, zenen mir gekumen tsu undzere bakante nokh Varshe. UNK

212
00:12:55,063 --> 00:12:58,921
dos iz shoyn geven vinter f- nayntsn hundert fertsik?

213
00:12:57,260 --> 00:13:04,215
dos iz geven der nayn der... dos iz geven der nayn un draysik in GRUDZIEŃ, dos iz detsember.

214
00:13:02,303 --> 00:13:04,119
GRUDZIEŃ, detsember.

215
00:13:04,215 --> 00:13:06,380
detsember iz gevezn, yo.

216
00:13:06,387 --> 00:13:11,480
zenen mir dort ge- geshlofn oyf di podloges, m'iz geshlofn, me hot zikh ah

217
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:17,063
m'iz geven mid fun dem veg, fun azoy fil geyn, hot men zikh yeder oysgetsoygn oyf di

218
00:13:17,203 --> 00:13:22,648
oyf di RITSPAOT, un azoy zenen mir gelegn, gevart.

219
00:13:22,705 --> 00:13:28,892
un undzere mener vos zenen geforn dort, di di mener vos hobn genumen dem vogn

220
00:13:28,892 --> 00:13:34,391
un un hot men zey ⟨bahal-⟩ farhaltn far NOWY DWÓR far Varshe

221
00:13:34,391 --> 00:13:37,447
un me hot zey dort ul- untergezukht, me hot dort

222
00:13:37,470 --> 00:13:40,316
hot men zey ale SOWIESO tsugenumen

223
00:13:40,322 --> 00:13:43,522
un zey hobn, zey hobn gelitn, me hot zey geshlogn,

224
00:13:43,849 --> 00:13:50,469
shoyn, dos iz shoyn geven di politsey, di di daytshe oder ikh veys nisht velkhe, di poylishe, ikh veys nisht velkhe politsey.

225
00:13:50,469 --> 00:13:55,385
me hot zey shoyn, un zenen gekumen zeyer in a shlekhtn tsushtand nokh Varshe.

226
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:58,861
un azoy hot men geven in Varshe biz di geto.

227
00:13:59,273 --> 00:14:02,287
biz di geto. vu hot ir gevoynt biz di geto? vu?

228
00:14:01,112 --> 00:14:09,688
⟨BE- geto -m⟩, in, mir grade hobn, ⟨ bay undz⟩ iz geven a oysnam, hot men nokh gehat tsu dingen a voynung, me hot nokh gevoynt in undzer voynung.

229
00:14:09,688 --> 00:14:13,191
ober di merheyt, zey hobn gevoynt in di shiln,

230
00:14:13,191 --> 00:14:14,659
in di...

231
00:14:14,659 --> 00:14:18,550
vos s'iz geven dort di, s'hot zikh, bote-midroshim,

232
00:14:16,992 --> 00:14:19,011
kehilishe pletser

233
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:23,507
i-, kehilishe pletser, un zey hobn zikh arayngetsoygn vayl zey hobn nisht gehat keyn gelt tsu batsoln.

234
00:14:23,507 --> 00:14:25,844
s'hot gekost... ikh veys nisht

235
00:14:26,155 --> 00:14:29,220
me hot, un un s'iz nisht geven tsu esn oykh nisht.

236
00:14:29,462 --> 00:14:32,901
un dort efsher hot men gegebn epes tsu esn, ikh veys nisht.

237
00:14:32,901 --> 00:14:36,274
ober yeder eyner a shtikl broyt iz geven gold.

238
00:14:36,567 --> 00:14:40,253
shoyn, vos yeder hot gehat az me hot gekont adurkhfirn,

239
00:14:40,253 --> 00:14:44,306
az me hot nokh gekont koyfn a shtikl broyt ⟨s'iz⟩ geven gut, ver hot gekont koyfn.

240
00:14:43,536 --> 00:14:45,808
dos iz nokh geven alts far dem geto.

241
00:14:45,257 --> 00:14:48,136
dos iz geven far di geto, efsher a yor tsayt.

242
00:14:46,506 --> 00:14:50,123
vos far a gzeyres gedenkt ir nokh far di geto akhuts dem

243
00:14:49,915 --> 00:14:56,160
v- a gze-, gzeyres, s'zenen geven a yedn tog, ikh bin dokh nisht geganen, froyen zenen iber hoypt nisht geganen.

244
00:14:50,123 --> 00:14:51,310
in Varshe?

245
00:14:54,657 --> 00:14:57,249
yo, ober vo- oyb ir gedenkt epes.

246
00:14:56,160 --> 00:14:58,290
mener zenen geganen tsu der arbet,

247
00:14:58,290 --> 00:15:00,877
me hot gekhapt di mener tsu der arbet.

248
00:15:01,137 --> 00:15:05,850
az a man ⟨zol⟩ aroysgeyn in di gas arayn, avade, mayn man iz oykhet, mayn zun iz shoyn geven

249
00:15:05,850 --> 00:15:12,605
a dervaksn yingl fun draytsn yor. er iz geven a heldish kind, geflegt geyn mit dem foter, hot men im oykhet genumen.

250
00:15:12,932 --> 00:15:22,494
eyn mol hot pasirt, me hot im gekhapt SOWIESO in di politsey, a gantse mayse gevezn, ikh veys nisht bizn hayntikn tog vos s'iz geven. me hot im gekhapt.

251
00:15:22,855 --> 00:15:26,015
a yidish kind hot men gekhapt, me hot nisht avekgeshikt

252
00:15:26,015 --> 00:15:27,219
me hot ⟨im⟩,

253
00:15:27,765 --> 00:15:31,724
me hot nor oysgeleyzt, me hot ⟨im⟩ aroysgenumen. shoyn.

254
00:15:32,254 --> 00:15:35,795
me hot gelitn tsores, s'iz nisht geven gut, s'iz geven zeyer shlekht.

255
00:15:35,795 --> 00:15:39,988
kh'fleg geyn a mol bazukhn in di shul arayn,

256
00:15:39,988 --> 00:15:43,149
dort vu mayne shkheynim zenen gevezn,

257
00:15:43,729 --> 00:15:50,087
iz geven geferlekh, s'hot ge- ge- gebushevet di di krankeytn,

258
00:15:50,087 --> 00:15:52,261
epidemyes zenen gevezn.

259
00:15:52,538 --> 00:15:56,601
tifus un vos mentshn zenen oysgeshtorbn, yedn tog iz geven.

260
00:15:56,601 --> 00:16:01,306
s'iz geven ⟨bay der⟩, adurkhtsugeyn in Varshe in di gas iz nisht ge- hot men nisht gekont adurkhgeyn.

261
00:16:00,503 --> 00:16:02,707
dos iz nokh geven far dem geto alts?

262
00:16:01,870 --> 00:16:04,001
dos iz geven nokh far di geto.

263
00:16:04,001 --> 00:16:09,862
iz shoyn gelegn fil, di harugim zenen gelegn tsugedekt mit a shtikl papir un dos iz gevezn.

264
00:16:09,885 --> 00:16:13,979
un nakher, s'iz geven di geto, kon men zikh shoyn forshteln vi s'iz gevezn.

265
00:16:14,037 --> 00:16:17,625
s'iz geven zeyer shlekht. undz hot men zikh aroysgeshmuglt fun di geto.

266
00:16:17,985 --> 00:16:19,705
me hot zikh aroysgeshmuglt.

267
00:16:18,559 --> 00:16:21,193
ober koydem hot men aykh arayngefirt in geto arayn?

268
00:16:20,955 --> 00:16:23,672
ah zikher, vos far a frage?

269
00:16:22,010 --> 00:16:23,940
vi lang ⟨dort⟩ ir geven in geto?

270
00:16:23,962 --> 00:16:26,158
ikh kle- undz ze'mir geven tsvey yor in Varshe.

271
00:16:26,052 --> 00:16:27,497
in geto.

272
00:16:26,186 --> 00:16:30,532
⟨mayne, az ikh bin⟩ geven a yor in geto, a yor iz men geven nokh far di geto.

273
00:16:30,287 --> 00:16:33,444
a yor far der geto un a yor in geto.

274
00:16:31,205 --> 00:16:34,149
yo, azoy UNK, azoy yo, ikh...

275
00:16:33,444 --> 00:16:38,482
heyst dos, in geto zent ir arayngegangen in eyn un fertsik?

276
00:16:37,009 --> 00:16:39,570
eyn un fertsikstn yor, yo.

277
00:16:38,691 --> 00:16:42,785
vos zhe kent ir mir dertseyln a bisl vegn vos gedenkt ir fun di geto-tsaytn?

278
00:16:42,542 --> 00:16:46,678
nu, vos kon ikh aykh fartseyln, s'iz geven zeyer shlekht, s'iz geven biter vi di gal.

279
00:16:46,678 --> 00:16:49,943
zeyer shlekht, shoyn. s'iz geven azoy shlekht,

280
00:16:49,943 --> 00:16:51,155
ikh gedenk...

281
00:16:51,313 --> 00:16:55,967
mayn man, mir hobn nokh gehat a bisele gelt, me hot nokh...

282
00:16:55,967 --> 00:16:58,684
s'iz undz gelungen, me hot dos adurkhgefirt.

283
00:16:58,684 --> 00:17:01,888
s'iz geven ⟨azelkhe⟩, bay mayn shvoger hot men ales tsugenumen.

284
00:17:01,894 --> 00:17:05,195
un undz iz gelungen, me hot es shabes adurkhgefirt.

285
00:17:06,146 --> 00:17:10,612
hot me-, hot men nokh ge- epes gekoyft, un me hot nokh epes gekokht oykhet.

286
00:17:11,108 --> 00:17:13,535
iz ikh gedenk ⟨iz⟩ tsugekumen arayn tsu mir,

287
00:17:13,535 --> 00:17:23,432
zenen gekumen fun undzer shtetl mentshn vos kh'hob zey nisht derkent. in aza kurtser tsayt s'iz nisht geven keyn mentshn, s'iz geven shkeletn, nisht keyn mentshn koym,

288
00:17:23,432 --> 00:17:25,867
un ⟨zey⟩ tsugekumen zenen geven vild,

289
00:17:25,890 --> 00:17:34,232
oysgehungert, un ⟨zey⟩ tsugelofn tsu di ⟨kukh un⟩ zey hobn gekhapt aroys vos s'iz geven in di in in in tepl vos s'iz nor gevezn.

290
00:17:34,232 --> 00:17:37,832
un ikh hob mamesh far di zelbe mentshn hob ikh moyre gehat.

291
00:17:38,007 --> 00:17:40,009
far mentshn vos nekhtn, vos

292
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:45,577
iz men gevezn di beste gute-fraynd in shtetl, ales iz geven undzere mentshn.

293
00:17:45,583 --> 00:17:47,551
mentshn, iz geven zeyer vild.

294
00:17:48,587 --> 00:17:52,158
dos iz der hunger, der noyt, di tsores hobn dos gebrengt.

295
00:17:52,772 --> 00:17:59,651
ot azoy iz geven, azoy iz geganen, biz in a, eynem a tog hot mayn man oysgezukht ⟨ot⟩ emetsn

296
00:17:59,995 --> 00:18:04,039
un m'iz adurkh durkh di ployt, mit di kinder m'iz adurkh.

297
00:18:03,285 --> 00:18:04,916
emetser hot aykh geholfn?

298
00:18:04,247 --> 00:18:07,779
s- es iz azoy geven:

299
00:18:07,779 --> 00:18:13,711
di, di kinder's eltern zenen geven in a, nokh biz s'iz geven di daytshe REICH

300
00:18:13,711 --> 00:18:15,862
iz nokh nisht geven keyn geto dort.

301
00:18:15,862 --> 00:18:18,382
hot men undz dort ahingefirt.

302
00:18:18,490 --> 00:18:20,351
m'hot undz nisht gefirt.

303
00:18:20,351 --> 00:18:23,945
zey hobn gevolt az me zol dort kumen, ahin.

304
00:18:23,945 --> 00:18:29,789
di shvester mi- mayne iz geforn vayl zi hot, geve- azoy vi a kristin hot zi oysgezen, a blonde.

305
00:18:29,222 --> 00:18:31,258
di shvester vos fun Daytshland gekumen?

306
00:18:30,032 --> 00:18:33,691
di, Daytshland, yo. iz zi geforn befor.

307
00:18:33,691 --> 00:18:37,918
der sh- der shvoger mayner iz shoyn geven a rikhtiker yid. er iz shoyn geven

308
00:18:37,918 --> 00:18:39,934
oysgezen azoy, a rikhtiker yid.

309
00:18:39,934 --> 00:18:44,094
hot mayn shvester di di ⟨me hot ir⟩ geshikt a kristin,

310
00:18:44,094 --> 00:18:45,748
a rikhtike kristin.

311
00:18:45,748 --> 00:18:48,284
un m'hot dem farshtelt far a ⟨goy, yo⟩,

312
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:55,558
dem shvoger, un zi hot im ibergefirt. azoy az zey zenen nisht geven baym, dort dem GOSTYNIN, in dem shtetl.

313
00:18:55,716 --> 00:19:00,495
vi a v- vi iz aykh gelungen aroystsugeyn fun geto? me hot dokh bavakht di geto, yo?

314
00:18:58,831 --> 00:19:02,560
vi, yo, m'hot, m'hot bavakht di geto un s'iz

315
00:19:01,340 --> 00:19:03,330
ir hot gedarft epes batsoln oder vos?

316
00:19:02,560 --> 00:19:06,607
s'iz kh've-, dos hot mayn man gemakht. ikh veys nisht vi dos iz gevezn.

317
00:19:04,778 --> 00:19:06,915
ir veyst nit..

318
00:19:06,616 --> 00:19:08,024
ikh veys er hot gezogt

319
00:19:08,024 --> 00:19:12,121
"makhst, host nokh epes, leyg arayn in epes a pekele,

320
00:19:12,121 --> 00:19:13,910
nem tsuzamen vos s'iz do,

321
00:19:13,910 --> 00:19:16,230
mir geyen haynt adurkh di geto".

322
00:19:16,708 --> 00:19:20,110
un me vet geyn tsu fus dort ahin in dem shtetl.

323
00:19:20,134 --> 00:19:22,726
vi zhe zent ir ongekumen take? in...

324
00:19:22,196 --> 00:19:26,962
zenen mir ar- zenen mir zeyer shlekht... azoy iz geven, m'iz aroys fun di geto,

325
00:19:27,103 --> 00:19:29,392
zenen mir adurkh dem ployt,

326
00:19:29,517 --> 00:19:32,413
hot mayn man gezen forn a kotsh.

327
00:19:32,942 --> 00:19:35,598
in Varshe zenen geven kotshn azelkhe.

328
00:19:35,018 --> 00:19:35,656
yo,

329
00:19:35,656 --> 00:19:37,510
yo, yo, yo, yo.

330
00:19:35,878 --> 00:19:37,340
ir veyst vos a kotsh iz?

331
00:19:37,363 --> 00:19:40,482
mit di yo, hot er ge- hot er gerufn

332
00:19:40,482 --> 00:19:43,121
un iz ahergekumen, mir ale zenen arayn.

333
00:19:43,121 --> 00:19:45,090
un dort, un er hot batsolt

334
00:19:45,090 --> 00:19:48,210
vifl ⟨undzer...⟩ me hot dokh geheysn gebn az me zol undz aroysfirn

335
00:19:48,271 --> 00:19:51,397
fun di geto, me zol undz aroysfirn oyf a veg.

336
00:19:51,775 --> 00:19:54,216
hot gezogt vi me zol undz firn

337
00:19:54,222 --> 00:19:56,713
un dort vet men shoyn aleynt geyn.

338
00:19:57,327 --> 00:20:00,578
der hot undz oyfgenumen oyfn veg,

339
00:20:00,972 --> 00:20:04,459
hot mayn man gezen epes s'iz nisht der rikhtiker veg.

340
00:20:04,819 --> 00:20:07,381
mayn man iz geven a zeyer a spritner.

341
00:20:07,381 --> 00:20:10,162
ir veyst vos a spritner iz? a zeyer a feiker.

342
00:20:08,143 --> 00:20:10,433
yo, yo, yo.

343
00:20:10,287 --> 00:20:15,520
un er hot zikh oryentirt in di zakhn, hot er gezen, epes dos iz nisht der veg

344
00:20:15,520 --> 00:20:16,840
vos me firt undz.

345
00:20:16,949 --> 00:20:18,476
s'iz nisht der rikhtiker.

346
00:20:18,476 --> 00:20:20,560
hot er ongehoybn tsu shrayen.

347
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:23,952
azoy vi mayn man hot geshrign, hobn mir ale geshrign.

348
00:20:23,952 --> 00:20:27,577
ikh un mayne dray di kinder hobn geshrign, ale dray.

349
00:20:27,651 --> 00:20:30,280
kh'hob dokh nokh gehat, ikh hob dokh a zun oykhet gehat.

350
00:20:30,280 --> 00:20:34,466
hot men ale geshrign, me hot azelkhene gevaldn gemakht, me hot azoy geshrign

351
00:20:34,466 --> 00:20:40,031
un yo, un m'hot, er hot gezen vi eyner loyft aroyf oyf di trep fun di kotsh

352
00:20:40,054 --> 00:20:43,153
hot er gezen. azoy vi s'iz, me hot geshrign,

353
00:20:43,176 --> 00:20:47,034
hot men o-, hot zikh dort, ergets iz geven a koshtshol

354
00:20:47,412 --> 00:20:53,979
aza, dos zenen geven di nones hobn zey geheysn, di frume shvesters.

355
00:20:51,626 --> 00:20:52,109
yo

356
00:20:53,624 --> 00:20:54,345
yo, yo.

357
00:20:53,979 --> 00:20:56,730
un ge- hobn dort gevoynt. hobn zey gezen,

358
00:20:56,730 --> 00:20:59,837
hobn gehert di gevaldn, zenen zey aroys.

359
00:20:59,837 --> 00:21:03,622
zey zenen aroys, zenen di tsvey vos hobn undz ba-

360
00:21:03,730 --> 00:21:07,656
ge- aroyfgeshprungen oyf di trepn, ⟨tsvey zenen⟩ oyfgeshprungen.

361
00:21:07,662 --> 00:21:12,864
eyner vos iz geforn mit di kotsh iz geven un tsvey ⟨shgotsim⟩ zenen aroyfgeshprungen.

362
00:21:12,864 --> 00:21:17,766
hobn zey gegebn a khap di peklekh vos mir hobn gehat. ikh hob gehat a tukh oyf mir,

363
00:21:17,766 --> 00:21:24,412
aza groys tukh. aropgekhapt mir dos tukh un di peklekh vos mir hobn gehat un zenen ⟨h⟩antlofn.

364
00:21:24,604 --> 00:21:27,571
hot zikh der goy opgeshtelt un mir zenen arop.

365
00:21:27,571 --> 00:21:31,027
mir zenen arop, zenen mir ahin dort tsu di nones.

366
00:21:31,337 --> 00:21:35,010
mir zenen ahin, zogn zey "du veyst vi me hot ⟨aykh do⟩ gefirt?

367
00:21:35,083 --> 00:21:37,510
m'hot enk gefirt in a veldl arayn.

368
00:21:37,510 --> 00:21:40,832
do firt men ale vos tsum, vos me harget zey oys".

369
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:44,122
un dos zenen geven polyakn? dos zenen geven polyakn.

370
00:21:41,620 --> 00:21:42,919
di nones hobn undz...

371
00:21:42,919 --> 00:21:46,167
yo, dos hobn di nones undz gezogt, di shvester,

372
00:21:46,167 --> 00:21:47,770
di frume shvester.

373
00:21:47,770 --> 00:21:50,704
MIŁOSIERNE PANNY zey hobn zey geheysn,

374
00:21:50,760 --> 00:21:52,491
hobn undz dos gezogt.

375
00:21:52,491 --> 00:21:56,728
"gut", zogt zi, "az ir hot gemakht gevaldn, az nisht, me hot enk opgeratevet yetst".

376
00:21:57,797 --> 00:21:59,175
 iz shoyn.

377
00:21:59,316 --> 00:22:04,156
"vu vilt ets geyn?" hot zi mir gezogt, zey hobn dokh farshtanen az m'iz aroys fun di geto

378
00:22:04,156 --> 00:22:05,616
un me vil ergets geyn.

379
00:22:05,616 --> 00:22:09,311
zogt zi "vos kon ikh, kon ⟨men undz enk⟩ helfn?"

380
00:22:09,311 --> 00:22:13,740
undz kon men gor nisht helfn. "do nemts, ⟨do⟩ geyts ⟨do, do⟩.

381
00:22:13,740 --> 00:22:19,849
efsher vet er, vet ets hobn tsu ton an altn mentsh, alte mentshn, nisht keyn yunge zol undz nisht nemen.

382
00:22:19,849 --> 00:22:22,980
nemts a dorozhke zol enk firn aroys oyf a veg.

383
00:22:22,980 --> 00:22:25,584
vi ets vilt geyn, shpeter vet ets shoyn geyn".

384
00:22:25,978 --> 00:22:27,401
azoy iz geven.

385
00:22:27,401 --> 00:22:29,802
hot men genumen vider a dorozhke.

386
00:22:30,012 --> 00:22:31,845
un m'iz aroys

387
00:22:32,222 --> 00:22:33,836
un m'iz geganen.

388
00:22:33,977 --> 00:22:39,408
iz azoy geven. ikh hob geganen me zol nisht geyn azoy fil, me zol UNK fardekhtikt

389
00:22:39,408 --> 00:22:41,770
mit mayne, mit di tsvey meydelekh.

390
00:22:41,770 --> 00:22:44,417
un mayn man iz geganen mitn zun.

391
00:22:44,473 --> 00:22:47,555
undz zenen mir adurkh, ⟨me hot⟩ geganen a tog un a nakht,

392
00:22:47,697 --> 00:22:49,642
a gantse tog un a nakht.

393
00:22:49,642 --> 00:22:53,059
un mayn man iz geganen oykhet azoy,

394
00:22:53,059 --> 00:22:57,124
ober er iz geganen oyf an andern veg un undz ze'mir geganen an andern veg.

395
00:22:57,282 --> 00:22:59,604
mayn man hot men gekhapt mitn zun.

396
00:23:00,572 --> 00:23:01,733
me hot im gekhapt.

397
00:23:01,733 --> 00:23:03,216
iz shoyn nisht vikhtik,

398
00:23:03,728 --> 00:23:05,986
zey hobn gehat mazl, me hot zey opgelozt.

399
00:23:05,986 --> 00:23:08,509
undz hot men nisht gekhapt un m'iz gegan-

400
00:23:08,509 --> 00:23:12,154
un shtelt aykh for, mir zenen gekumen oyfn plats

401
00:23:12,154 --> 00:23:15,615
do vu me hot gezolt kumen, un mayn man iz gekumen oyfn plats.

402
00:23:15,615 --> 00:23:22,177
in dem shtetl, s'iz nokh nisht geven dos rikhtike shtetl, a shtetl befor, zenen mir arayn dort,

403
00:23:22,177 --> 00:23:26,851
m'hot gezen vi me firt di yidn tsu der arbet. hot men shoyn gezen az dos iz es.

404
00:23:26,851 --> 00:23:30,183
m'hot dort gehat oykhet mishpokhe un zey hobn undz arayngenumen,

405
00:23:30,183 --> 00:23:35,058
nakher iz men arayn tsu di shvester, un azoy iz men geven mit di shvester iz men shoyn gevezn

406
00:23:35,672 --> 00:23:39,205
biz, biz, biz a-, biz aroys fun UNK

407
00:23:36,887 --> 00:23:39,952
vu? in in velkhe shtetl? in GUSTANIN?

408
00:23:39,816 --> 00:23:43,178
di ah, yo, in GOSTYNIN, dos iz di mame gevezn,

409
00:23:43,178 --> 00:23:47,085
zi hot dort gevoynt, un zi hot nisht gevoynt ⟨hot⟩ zi iz oykhet dort ahin.

410
00:23:47,085 --> 00:23:50,988
vayl zey hobn gehat dort a shvoger ⟨vu der,⟩ der man hot gehat a bruder.

411
00:23:51,096 --> 00:23:56,189
hot er, hobn zey dort gevoynt, zenen zey dort ahin un undz zenen mir vider tsu zey ahin.

412
00:23:56,189 --> 00:23:58,093
azoy iz men shoyn geven tsuzamen.

413
00:23:58,116 --> 00:24:03,926
mit sh- dray shvester zenen mir geven tsuzamen. ikh un di daytshe, fun Daytshland,

414
00:23:58,285 --> 00:23:59,809
in ye-, dos iz shoyn,

415
00:24:01,005 --> 00:24:02,020
dos iz shoyn ge-

416
00:24:03,926 --> 00:24:08,824
un di, ir muter, iz men geven dray shvester tsuzamen. nu shoyn.

417
00:24:08,157 --> 00:24:10,723
⟨un⟩ di di in yene tsay-, dos iz shoyn geven ven?

418
00:24:10,723 --> 00:24:14,221
s'iz nokh alts geven in eyn un fertsik tsi s'iz shoyn geven in tsvey un fer-

419
00:24:12,983 --> 00:24:14,944
s'iz shoyn in tsvey un fertsikstn.

420
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:19,575
tsvey un fertsikstn yor. un demolt s'iz shoyn in in GOST- GOSTANIAN, vi hot ir geheysn?

421
00:24:15,413 --> 00:24:16,385
ya.

422
00:24:18,737 --> 00:24:20,173
GOSTYNIN, GOSTYNIN.

423
00:24:19,800 --> 00:24:21,586
GOSTYNIN.

424
00:24:20,715 --> 00:24:21,837
GOSTYNIN yo.

425
00:24:21,586 --> 00:24:25,245
dem- demolt iz shoyn geven a geto dortn oder dortn iz nisht geven keyn ge-

426
00:24:23,968 --> 00:24:26,763
iz geven, undz, iz men gekumen iz yo shoyn geven di geto

427
00:24:26,763 --> 00:24:29,564
in di tsvey un fertsikstn yor iz shoyn geven di geto.

428
00:24:28,423 --> 00:24:30,090
shoyn yo geven di geto.

429
00:24:29,753 --> 00:24:31,698
tsvey un fertsikstn iz shoyn geven.

430
00:24:30,090 --> 00:24:34,947
hot men aykh vayter arayngefirt in geto arayn O ir hot geven nakher, nakher, nisht gevoynt in geto?

431
00:24:33,385 --> 00:24:37,198
yo, m'hot gevoynt in di geto, zikher, arayn.

432
00:24:37,198 --> 00:24:41,245
di shvester hot oykh nisht gevoynt aleynt, zi hot oykh dort gevoynt a, a mishpokhe.

433
00:24:41,245 --> 00:24:44,780
azoy az di di geto iz nisht ⟨geven⟩, nisht gevoynt eyner aleyn.

434
00:24:43,189 --> 00:24:44,803
shoyn geven demoltst di geto.

435
00:24:44,780 --> 00:24:48,625
nu, s'iz shoyn geven di geto, vayl zi hot oykh gevoynt mit nokh a mishpokhe.

436
00:24:48,625 --> 00:24:50,794
un undz zenen mir oykh gekumen tsun ir.

437
00:24:50,833 --> 00:24:53,932
ober ⟨zint ikh⟩ mayn shvester iz geganen tsu der arbet

438
00:24:54,107 --> 00:24:58,550
arb-, ale zenen geganen tsu der arbet. ikh bin nisht geganen tsu der arbet, ikh bin shoyn geven nisht di...

439
00:24:58,550 --> 00:25:00,542
ober undz zenen mir lang nisht geven.

440
00:25:00,542 --> 00:25:05,492
fun yener geto, fun GOSTYNIN, zenen mir nokh STRZEGOWO

441
00:25:05,835 --> 00:25:10,203
ober di shvester fun Daytshland hot men genumen fun di gas arop.

442
00:25:10,203 --> 00:25:11,268
azoy a-

443
00:25:10,608 --> 00:25:11,871
in GOSTYNIN?

444
00:25:11,555 --> 00:25:12,411
in GOSTYNIN.

445
00:25:12,552 --> 00:25:15,060
zey hob ikh, zi hob ikh nisht gezen shoyn

446
00:25:15,100 --> 00:25:17,153
de- fun der geto.

447
00:25:17,513 --> 00:25:18,216
yo.

448
00:25:18,255 --> 00:25:21,252
vi lang zent ir geven in GOSTYNIN in geto?

449
00:25:20,753 --> 00:25:23,272
iz nisht geven lang, ikh bin geven a por khadoshim.

450
00:25:23,272 --> 00:25:28,060
nisht lang, nisht lang, ikh meyn az s'iz nokh geven ⟨farn dray un fertsikstn⟩.

451
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:30,250
ir gedenkt epes faln tsu dertseyln? vos s'iz, vi s'iz geven geto GOSTYNIN?

452
00:25:29,325 --> 00:25:31,100
vu? in GOSTYNIN?

453
00:25:30,690 --> 00:25:32,610
vi hot zikh gefirt dortn ⟨dos geto⟩?

454
00:25:31,964 --> 00:25:34,820
oykhet dos zelbe. s'iz geven a JUDENRAT

455
00:25:34,995 --> 00:25:39,763
un m'hot genumen ale tog tsu der arbet, un m'hot ale tog avekgeshikt mentshn.

456
00:25:39,763 --> 00:25:44,864
dort hot men gekhapt mayn zun. dort hot men gekhapt mayn man un me hot im avekgeshikt

457
00:25:44,864 --> 00:25:47,508
fun GOSTYNIN. mayn zun hot men avekgeshikt,

458
00:25:47,508 --> 00:25:50,683
maynem a shvoger hot men avekgeshikt, tsvey shvoger!

459
00:25:51,600 --> 00:25:55,711
ir hot gehat epes a anung vu me nemt di mentshn? vu me shikt zey avek?

460
00:25:54,813 --> 00:25:59,098
neyn, m'hot nisht gehat keyn shum anung. m'hot gezogt az me shikt zey avek ah tsu der arbet.

461
00:25:59,098 --> 00:26:02,242
ober vu me shikt zey hot men nisht gehat keyn shum anung.

462
00:26:02,502 --> 00:26:07,189
eyn mol s'iz mayn shvoger, eyner iz er tsurikgekumen, iz antlofn, ir foter,

463
00:26:07,189 --> 00:26:11,838
un un nakher, in tsvey-dray tog hot men im vider gekhapt, me hot im vider avekgeshikt.

464
00:26:11,838 --> 00:26:13,751
ober er iz nisht shoyn nisht tsurikgekumen.

465
00:26:13,909 --> 00:26:18,809
vi hot zikh dortn take gefirt der JUDENRAT un di yid-, s'hot geven yidishe politsey oykh, neyn?

466
00:26:18,050 --> 00:26:24,762
yo, ales ⟨iz⟩ s'iz geven yidishe politsey, s'iz geven yidishe, vos hobn zey gefirt. besof hot men ale avekgeshikt.

467
00:26:24,762 --> 00:26:28,297
s'iz nisht geblibn keyn eyne. ⟨geganen tsu di JUDENRAT⟩.

468
00:26:26,423 --> 00:26:30,711
ober vos gedenkt ir? vi hobn zey zikh gefirt mit mi- mi- mit di yidn demoltstn?

469
00:26:30,885 --> 00:26:36,380
me zogt az gut, ikh veys. ikh ⟨bin mir keyn mol nisht gevekht⟩, ikh bin nisht geven bay der arbet. ikh veys nisht.

470
00:26:36,268 --> 00:26:40,705
zent ir nor, me hot avekgenumen ayer man, me hot avekgenumen di ale mentshn vos ir hot gezogt,

471
00:26:39,795 --> 00:26:41,139
yo, yo.

472
00:26:40,705 --> 00:26:43,096
ver zhe iz geblibn mit aykh demoltstn?

473
00:26:42,445 --> 00:26:45,968
mit mir iz geblibn di tsveyte shvester, ir mame,

474
00:26:45,968 --> 00:26:50,572
un ire kinder dray, un mayne dray k-, mayne tsvey kinder.

475
00:26:50,359 --> 00:26:53,441
vi hot ir zikh aleyn a eytse gegebn dortn in geto?

476
00:26:52,787 --> 00:26:54,101
ver? undz?

477
00:26:53,532 --> 00:26:54,471
yo.

478
00:26:54,270 --> 00:26:56,118
vi m'hot, m'iz nisht lang gevezn.

479
00:26:56,248 --> 00:27:00,781
me, m'iz nisht lang geven. bay mir iz azoy gevezn. ikh hob nokh gehat gelt.

480
00:27:01,885 --> 00:27:03,397
hob ikh nokh gekoyft.

481
00:27:03,623 --> 00:27:08,257
mayn tokhter di di eltere tokhter hot oysgezen vi a shikse.

482
00:27:08,871 --> 00:27:10,485
punkt vi a shikse.

483
00:27:10,828 --> 00:27:13,769
oyf ir hot men nisht gegleybt. afile keyn Varshe

484
00:27:13,769 --> 00:27:16,053
iz zi aroysgeganen POZA geto

485
00:27:16,887 --> 00:27:20,290
aynkoyfn zakhn. a a blonde shiksele.

486
00:27:20,346 --> 00:27:21,808
azoy iz zi geven.

487
00:27:22,624 --> 00:27:27,160
iz zi geganen, zi iz geven zeyer a ODWAŻNA, a gutn poylish hot zi geredt,

488
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:31,410
iz zi aroysgeganen, hot ayngekoyft. un azoy iz geven do in di geto oykhet.

489
00:27:31,635 --> 00:27:34,021
zi iz geganen, zi hot undz ayngekoyft.

490
00:27:34,021 --> 00:27:38,505
m'hot nisht gekoyft keyn groyse zakhn. vos iz geven dos koyf- vos hot men den gekrign?

491
00:27:37,552 --> 00:27:39,211
me zol kenen ekzistirn a bisl.

492
00:27:38,505 --> 00:27:41,782
me zol konen lebn. a bisl kartofl, a bisl kroyt.

493
00:27:41,782 --> 00:27:45,984
ikh veys vos s'iz geven, a shikl broyt iz geve- ah ef- shvarts efsher.

494
00:27:45,984 --> 00:27:47,221
kh'gedenk nisht.

495
00:27:48,173 --> 00:27:52,067
m'hot, keyn fleysh hot men nisht gegesn.

496
00:27:52,067 --> 00:27:56,166
keyn, kukhn hot men nisht gebakn.

497
00:27:56,391 --> 00:28:03,371
m'hot gelebt vi m'hot gekont ⟨UNK krom UNK tsu⟩ kumen dos bisl lebn, oyb me hot gehat a shtikl broyt iz geven gut, mit a kartofl.

498
00:28:03,681 --> 00:28:05,143
azoy hot men gelebt.

499
00:28:05,284 --> 00:28:09,626
un nakher hot men shoyn, hot men... di tokhter mayne take,

500
00:28:09,626 --> 00:28:12,281
di shikse, s'iz ⟨du veyst⟩ a shikse,

501
00:28:12,338 --> 00:28:15,676
iz zi iz, zi iz geven zeyer ODWAŻNA un zi iz geganen,

502
00:28:15,676 --> 00:28:17,427
zi iz mit im geganen,

503
00:28:17,451 --> 00:28:20,044
un zi iz aroysgeganen fun der geto

504
00:28:20,978 --> 00:28:25,277
un ah ah eyn mol ven zi kumt aheym zogt zi "mame, du veyst vos?

505
00:28:25,277 --> 00:28:30,067
s'iz nokh do, s'iz nokh do a geto in STRZEGOWO".

506
00:28:30,124 --> 00:28:34,151
un dos shmuest men yetst, m'hot yedn tog geshmuest m'et aroysshikn.

507
00:28:34,663 --> 00:28:37,492
un, un bay undz iz nokh geven nokh a meydl baym,

508
00:28:37,492 --> 00:28:40,933
i- ir mame bay di di meydl's mame do.

509
00:28:40,941 --> 00:28:44,884
di shvester mayne hot gehat ⟨a mol⟩ genumen in SKĘPE

510
00:28:44,991 --> 00:28:49,190
a yesoyme vos zi hot nisht gehat keyn foter un keyn muter.

511
00:28:49,190 --> 00:28:51,341
hot zi zikh genumen dos meydl

512
00:28:51,341 --> 00:28:55,362
un bay zikh in di shtub arayn ah, ot, ah.

513
00:28:55,386 --> 00:28:57,034
a rakhmones.

514
00:28:57,107 --> 00:29:01,438
un dos meydl hot gehat in STRZEGOWO mishpokhe.

515
00:29:02,119 --> 00:29:05,842
un m'hot gezogt az STRZEGOWO redt men nokh nisht vegn aroysshikn.

516
00:29:06,169 --> 00:29:10,652
zi zogt "veyst, mame, zol men nemen, me zol forn nokh STRZEGOWO".

517
00:29:10,675 --> 00:29:14,297
mayn tokhter! ikh hob, zogt zi, "gey, ikh vel dingen a goy,

518
00:29:14,708 --> 00:29:17,554
UNK", zogt zi, "nemen un m'et ale ahin.

519
00:29:18,538 --> 00:29:21,412
vos vet zayn vet zayn". un azoy iz geven.

520
00:29:21,412 --> 00:29:25,231
zi iz geganen, zi hot gebrengt a goy un m'hot zikh oyfgezetst un m'iz geforn.

521
00:29:25,339 --> 00:29:28,998
nokh STRZEGOWO, dos iz geven dos, ikh

522
00:29:28,998 --> 00:29:31,512
mit mayne kinder un di meydl

523
00:29:31,512 --> 00:29:36,642
un di, mayn shvester mit di kinder, vayl di dem Daytshland iz shoyn nisht geven.

524
00:29:36,642 --> 00:29:38,247
dos iz nokh geven nokh a

525
00:29:38,248 --> 00:29:40,874
di daytshl hot dort gehat a tokhter oykhet.

526
00:29:40,982 --> 00:29:44,244
m'hot di tokhter oykh mitgenumen, zi iz oykh mit undz mit,

527
00:29:44,244 --> 00:29:48,435
ober zi iz fun STRZEGOWO avekgeganen, zi iz mer nisht shoyn nisht aheymgekumen.

528
00:29:48,762 --> 00:29:52,083
oy, me kon nisht ales dertseyln nokh, kh'kon nisht ales azoy...

529
00:29:51,141 --> 00:29:54,057
yo. zaynt ir ongekumen keyn STRZEGOWO...

